If it has like c for compile r for run etc… it’s not working for me either… so right click compile (or compiler w\e it is) and click edit erase all of it and replace it with this@echo off COLOR 09 title vitality compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_04\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause
